## Tech Stack

### Backend
- Python 3.12+ with FastAPI
- httpx for async HTTP
- structlog, slowapi for logging/rate limiting

### Frontend
- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite 5
- FleetSDK for Ergo transaction building
- ergo-lib-wasm-browser for WASM operations
- Nautilus EIP-12 wallet integration

### Blockchain
- Ergo Testnet
- ErgoTree smart contracts
- UTXO model with Sigma protocols

## Ports

| Service    | Port | Description                  |
|------------|------|------------------------------|
| Ergo Node  | 9052 | REST API, wallet, blockchain |
| Backend    | 8000 | FastAPI server               |
| Frontend   | 3000 | Vite dev server              |

## LP Liquidity Pool Endpoints

| Method | Path                                | Description                    |
|--------|-------------------------------------|--------------------------------|
| GET    | `/api/lp/pool`                      | Pool TVL, supply, price, stats |
| GET    | `/api/lp/price`                     | LP token price                 |
| GET    | `/api/lp/balance/{address}`         | LP balance for address         |
| GET    | `/api/lp/apy`                       | APY calculation                |
| GET    | `/api/lp/estimate/deposit`          | Deposit share estimate         |
| GET    | `/api/lp/estimate/withdraw`         | Withdraw ERG estimate          |
| POST   | `/api/lp/deposit`                   | Build deposit transaction      |
| POST   | `/api/lp/request-withdraw`          | Request withdrawal (cooldown)  |
| POST   | `/api/lp/execute-withdraw`          | Execute matured withdrawal     |
| POST   | `/api/lp/cancel-withdraw`           | Cancel pending withdrawal      |

